ji\" />咁我想問下，你男朋友覺得秋葉原定係池袋多野睇啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c39af0356850b6fe173bfb2c22c7869e3934cb4c","tid":291022,"uid":71949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T12:26:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直去飛田</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飛田有乜嘢好推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}